f:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Bright, bold, and unmistakably Flytrap. Gradients and character motifs help this card stand out in a contractor’s stack. The slogan “Helping your property thrive” ties everything back to the core mission.\n",["$","$La",null,{"src":"/work/flytrap/7.png","alt":"Lastly, a colorful business card that separates Flytrap Properties from the generic, featuring their full-color logo and business information.","caption":"Lastly, a colorful business card that separates Flytrap Properties from the generic, featuring their full-color logo and business information.","zoom":true}]]}]
10:["$","h2",null,{"children":"The Solution"}]
11:["$","p",null,{"children":"Flytrap Properties now has a playful, memorable identity system built to scale—from backyards to blueprints. The branding captures the spirit of local craftsmanship while standing apart from competitors. With a mascot full of character and cohesive visuals across touchpoints, Flytrap doesn’t just remodel homes—it redefines what a remodeling brand can look like."}]
